                            <comment id="15564406" author="stefania" created="Tue, 11 Oct 2016 04:16:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve changed the default value to zero, which has the same effect as changing it to -1, disabling the wait for pending tracing events. The tests already set &lt;tt&gt;cassandra.wait_for_tracing_events_timeout_secs&lt;/tt&gt; to 15 seconds, so they don&apos;t need changing.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In order to save CI resources, I&apos;ve launched the tests only on 2.2 and 3.X (which had conflicts):&lt;/p&gt;

